{"tid":724640,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"暑假第一次去台北 求plan","createTime":"2018-07-01T05:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T07:56:07.000Z","uid":182339,"like":0,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e3f4bce3c55cd0581e5266cf98ff09e3f1c941bf","tid":724640,"uid":182339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:48:11.000Z","msg":"暑假第一次同家人去台北 5days trip<br />\n我 我老婆 仔仔 我媽 我阿哥 同阿嫂六個<br />\n預左會包車 但係無咩頭緒邊度好去<br />\n有無巴打絲打去過台北可以比d意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家人偏愛海鮮 吃野 <br />\n只希望唔好個trip太趕<br />\n簡簡單單飲飲食食 行下特色景點都ok🙏🏻"},{"pid":"17c5146e8b8cda536fa1ea03d8ea1078c0bafbf7","tid":724640,"uid":28920,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:51:03.000Z","msg":"係咁意google下都一堆list啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6453644132b94db2b1bf213467e08cfdcf6eaf17","tid":724640,"uid":13514,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:51:46.000Z","msg":"伸手伸到你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd5f13bbf4f533c41d89fd8e2b33f492f90d597","tid":724640,"uid":101733,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T06:05:17.000Z","msg":"台北咋喎 自己做下功課啦 去旅行都去得咁懶"},{"pid":"ff70dab8db41c97c4321a78c93a4f160e89cfd25","tid":724640,"uid":106320,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T06:07:15.000Z","msg":"第一次 <br />\n一日淡水 西門叮<br />\n一日九份 十份<br />\n其他自己諗/問包車司機"},{"pid":"90212e7565f4e8e23858857e041dbd1154de08d8","tid":724640,"uid":182339,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T07:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/154205_3ed50cf609ee3b1f334e8595fa7ac013.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F154205_3ed50cf609ee3b1f334e8595fa7ac013.png&h=27fba493&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/0